{"tw": {"3633740": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "將異世界收入後宮!", "steam_appid": 3633740, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>【遊戲概要】</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3633740/extras/24221ed2d8f797d31e5716f1fd2a5e53.avif?t=1762480984\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3633740/extras_big/24221ed2d8f797d31e5716f1fd2a5e53.avif?t=1762480984 width=800 height=454 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >這是一款快節奏的RPG遊戲。主角朱莉的靈魂被魔神莉亞做成扶他魔物。 為了破壞女神莉絲的計畫，以及朱莉滿足自身的慾望，她開始闖蕩這個有著許多美麗可愛女性的異世界!。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>【遊戲玩法】</strong> </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>快速吞噬</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >除了劇情上需要或精英敵人外玩家無須進入戰鬥，碰撞就能快速吞噬比自己弱小的魔物並成長!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3633740/extras/00c816fe9a1aa019458ec6eaa2554638.poster.avif?t=1762480984\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3633740/extras/00c816fe9a1aa019458ec6eaa2554638.webm?t=1762480984\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3633740/extras/00c816fe9a1aa019458ec6eaa2554638.mp4?t=1762480984\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>精英敵人</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >完成困難的戰鬥後可以得到特殊物品，讓朱莉更輕鬆的橫行世界!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3633740/extras/5893931a