_item_assets/steam/apps/3633740/extras_big/24221ed2d8f797d31e5716f1fd2a5e53.avif?t=1762480984 width=800 height=454 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is a fast-paced RPG. The protagonist, Julie, has had her soul transformed into a Futanari monster by the demon goddess Lia. To thwart the plans of the goddess Liss—and to satisfy her own desires—Julie sets off on an adventure in a world filled with many beautiful and charming women!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >【Gameplay】</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Quick Devouring</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Aside from essential story battles and elite enemies, players don’t need to engage in traditional combat. Weaker monsters are instantly devoured upon collision, allowing Julie to grow stronger!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3633740/extras/5cbf9bf4651b59298878f2b6a6d6e694.poster.avif?t=1762480984\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3633740/extras/5cbf9bf4651b59298878f2b6a6d6e694.webm?t=1762480984\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3633740/extras/5cbf9bf4651b59298878f2b6a6d6e694.mp4?t=1762480984\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Elite Enemies</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Defeating tough enemies rewards special items that make it even easier for Julie to dominate the world!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3633740/extras/77e0cdb28d3901ef5e5250f24863b20d.avif?t=1762480984\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.st